## 6.1 Plotting Coffeechain Sales Report


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
report %>%
  group_by(Product) %>%
  summarize('Monthly Sales' = list(Sales), 
            .groups = "drop") %>%
   gt() %>%
   gt_plt_sparkline('Monthly Sales',
                    same_limit = FALSE)
```

